{"tid":846224,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"當自己尼馬　盧卡古插花笑死你","createTime":"2018-10-03T09:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T12:07:34.000Z","uid":4661,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c29d10b5e5d4b158779e8476d1fc9e6b84ea9054","tid":846224,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T09:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=JfXCIXuIG48\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJfXCIXuIG48&d=%2BX40yYmwoEG9YEvn5HZpUZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=050fa1a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=JfXCIXuIG48</a><br />\n<br />\n曼聯喺歐聯分組賽被華倫西亞悶和，除咗阿歷斯山齊士被插到開花之外，箭頭盧卡古亦都受到唔少批評，「紅魔鬼」名宿里奧費迪南就表示：「依家嘅盧卡古真係好容易Mark，一碌木咁企喺度，佢需要多啲走動去擾亂敵方防線。」 <br />\n<br />\n不過，里奧費迪南嘅意見又未必啱得晒，事關盧卡古今場上半場尾段，就曾經當自己係尼馬，喺禁區右邊企圖插花過人，點知插咗兩下，隻左腳唔小心踩咗落個波度，搞到個人去咗前面而個波喺身後，網民紛紛留言笑爆：「盧卡古插花係世界上最好笑嘅」、「插花插到自己唔知個波去咗邊，只有盧卡古先至做得到！」"},{"pid":"2d39b93c191eea385d381214e3f1673d9d1cc7a6","tid":846224,"uid":34293,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T09:16:58.000Z","msg":"拉輸福特開角球都夠晒好笑"},{"pid":"baea1c22b3763cc626f89e10b75002c590a54722","tid":846224,"uid":96894,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T09:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/KZSP43mfs8w06DviTC/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FKZSP43mfs8w06DviTC%2Fgiphy.gif&h=24265e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/161713_b80964ee4fe60d2d05a38e03311b0417.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F161713_b80964ee4fe60d2d05a38e03311b0417.gif&h=20ff865c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bcf7401cf66a30c881d560a0852f033dc0395c0","tid":846224,"uid":33770,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201